List resources

Source: R/S7_method_resources.R
list_resources.Rd

List resources

Usage

list_resources(x)

Arguments

x

Object of class careMain or careTemp

Value

A list of API resources

Examples

careMain("enrollees") |> list_resources()
#> # A tibble: 7 × 5
#>    year file                                                 size ext   download

#> 6  2024 Medicare FFS  Public Provider Enrollment Methodol…   0.36 pdf   https:/…
#> 7  2024 Medicare Fee-For-Service Public Provider Enrollme…   0.03 pdf   https:/…
